014package org.gbif.api.model.event.search;
015
016import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.annotation.JsonDeserialize;
017import org.gbif.api.model.common.paging.Pageable;
018import org.gbif.api.model.common.search.PredicateSearchRequest;
019import org.gbif.api.model.predicate.Predicate;
020
021/** Search request that uses a predicate filter like the ones used un downloads. */
022@JsonDeserialize(as = EventPredicateSearchRequest.class)
023public class EventPredicateSearchRequest extends EventSearchRequest
024    implements PredicateSearchRequest {
025
026  private Predicate predicate;
027
028  public EventPredicateSearchRequest() {}
029
030  public EventPredicateSearchRequest(Pageable page) {
031    super(page);
032  }
033
034  @Override
035  public Predicate getPredicate() {
036    return predicate;
037  }
038
039  @Override
040  public void setPredicate(Predicate predicate) {
041    this.predicate = predicate;
042  }
043}
